it isn't my son.

1360
01:28:00,358 --> 01:28:01,734
[Julian's dad] You wrote that, Julian?

1361
01:28:02,485 --> 01:28:03,903
Yes, sir.

1362
01:28:03,987 --> 01:28:07,240
