of a class photo.

1363
01:28:08,783 --> 01:28:11,035
Your son photoshopped Auggie out of it.

1364
01:28:14,455 --> 01:28:18,543
No. No, he didn't. I did.

1365
01:28:19,502 --> 01:28:21,754
Of course, I didn't think that
he would bring it to school.

1366
01:28:21,838 --> 01:28:23,840
But when our friends come over
and they see that picture,

1367
01:28:23,923 --> 01:28:25,967
