1380
01:29:06,090 --> 01:29:08,092
You'll stay home
from the nature preserve trip.

1381
01:29:08,176 --> 01:29:09,010
That's all.

1382
01:29:09,093 --> 01:29:12,680
Two days for a couple of notes from a kid?

1383
01:29:14,098 --> 01:29:16,434
After all the money that we
have poured into this school?

1384
01:29:17,018 --> 01:29:19,103
