on the school board, Mr Tushman.

1385
01:29:19,228 --> 01:29:20,354
Oh. [sighs]

1386
01:29:21,689 --> 01:29:23,316
[exhales] Well, I have more.

1387
01:29:23,900 --> 01:29:25,151
[Sarah] So, what would you have us do?

1388
01:29:25,234 --> 01:29:27,612
