single person in the world?

1389
01:29:29,238 --> 01:29:31,491
Nobody can get their feelings hurt ever?

1390
01:29:31,574 --> 01:29:34,911
[chuckles]
You are not doing these kids any favours.

1391
01:29:34,994 --> 01:29:38,831
[sighs] Mrs Albans,
Auggie can't change the way he looks.

1392
01:29:41,084 --> 01:29:43,920
So, maybe we can change the way we see.

1393
01:29:50,218 --> 01:29:51,094
[Sarah] Yes.

1394
01:29:51,260 --> 01:29:54,055
