1397
01:30:05,191 --> 01:30:08,694
-Mom. I have friends, Dad.
-[sighs]

1398
01:30:08,778 --> 01:30:09,654
[Julian's dad] Let's go, Julian.

1399
01:30:10,738 --> 01:30:12,073
Come on.

1400
01:30:19,247 --> 01:30:20,414
[Julian] Mr Tushman.

1401
01:30:24,043 --> 01:30:25,378
I'm really sorry.

1402
01:30:28,089 --> 01:30:29,966
I know you are, Julian.

1403
01:30:35,888 --> 01:30:37,890
[kids chattering excitedly]

1404
01:30:46,023 --> 01:30:48,442
-He's not even looking at us.
