-Thanks, guys.

1506
01:36:44,131 --> 01:36:45,674
You totally saved our butts.

1507
01:36:45,758 --> 01:36:47,343
Yeah, thanks, guys.

1508
01:36:50,596 --> 01:36:54,183
You know, it was cool
how you stood your ground, little dude.

